#. +> trunk5
#: content/bug-triaging.md:14
msgid "One of the most helpful and important things you can do to help is **bug triaging**. The goal is to save developers from doing this. It helps them fix bugs more quickly and use their precious time to develop exciting new features for Kdenlive."
