#. +> trunk5
#: content/bug-triaging.md:16
msgid "That’s where you come in! If you are a reasonably experienced Kdenlive user and want to help out, here is how to get ready and set up. Help with bug triaging is a real and lasting contribution to Kdenlive. Remember that the dev team is made up of volunteers. And if you benefit from the work others did on Kdenlive, helping with bug triaging is a great opportunity to give something back to the project!"
msgstr ""

