#: content/fund/index.md:0
msgid "About Kdenlive"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/fund/index.md:0
msgid ""
"Kdenlive is a community project which aims to deliver a free and open source video editing software to allow everybody to produce high quality content.\n"
"\n"
"The project is part of the KDE Community and developed by a small, mostly volunteer team from all over the world.\n"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/fund/index.md:0
msgid "Other Ways to Contribute"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/fund/index.md:0
msgid "If money is tight, you can still make a big difference by contributing your time and skills! No programming experience is needed – there are plenty of ways to get involved, like help with testing, bug triaging, and of course providing code snippets and fixes for bugs!"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/get-involved.md:9
msgid "Kdenlive is an open-source project that thrives on community contributions. As a free and open-source video editor, we believe in the power of collaborative development. Whether you're a developer, translator, documentation writer, or user, your contributions can help make Kdenlive better for everyone. Join our vibrant community and be part of shaping the future of open-source video editing!"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/get-involved.md:11
msgid "{{< card-grid >}} {{< card title=\"Development\" link=\"https://invent.kde.org/multimedia/kdenlive#developer-information\" buttonText=\"Learn More\" >}} Help improve Kdenlive's codebase, fix bugs, and implement new features. Join our development community and contribute to the core functionality. {{< /card >}}"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/get-involved.md:16
msgid "{{< card title=\"Translations\" link=\"https://l10n.kde.org/\" buttonText=\"Learn More\" >}} Help make Kdenlive available in your language. Join our translation team and help localize the application or its manual for users worldwide. {{< /card >}}"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/get-involved.md:20
msgid "{{< card title=\"Documentation\" link=\"https://community.kde.org/Kdenlive/Workgroup/Documentation\" buttonText=\"Learn More\" >}} Improve user guides, write tutorials, and help create comprehensive documentation to help users get the most out of Kdenlive. {{< /card >}}"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/get-involved.md:24
msgid "{{< card title=\"Bug Triaging\" link=\"/bug-triaging\" buttonText=\"Learn More\" >}} Help identify, verify, and prioritize bug reports. Your help in managing issues makes the development process more efficient. {{< /card >}}"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/get-involved.md:28
msgid "{{< card title=\"Bug Reporting\" link=\"/bug-reports\" buttonText=\"Learn More\" >}} Found an issue? Help us improve by reporting bugs and providing detailed information about problems you encounter. {{< /card >}}"
msgstr ""

#. +> trunk5
#: content/get-involved.md:32
msgid "{{< card title=\"Donations\" link=\"/fund\" buttonText=\"Learn More\" >}} Support Kdenlive's development by making a donation. Your financial contribution helps maintain infrastructure and fund development. {{< /card >}} {{< /card-grid >}}"
msgstr ""

